ISLAMABAD, Jan 15 (APP):Minister for Information and Broadcasting Chaudhry Fawad Hussain on Saturday tweeted a picture of blossomed mustard field from Chakwal.
He said mustard fields were in full bloom across Chakwal, a city of Rawalpindi division.“May the Almighty keep the fields and orchards of Pakistan inhabited forever,” he added.
